    <description>A kit of replicating mechanites, compounds and canisters complete with a wide barreled launcher. The canisters release chemical clouds on impact producing various effects. \n\nReinforcer clouds latch onto creatures and buildings, temporarily reinforcing their armor and repairing damage respectivly. \n\nOxidizer clouds corrode structures and embrittle armor, causing successful hits to deal more damage than normal. \n\nFirestarter canisters drench the area with a thick layer of fuel before sparking it alight, while the initial blast does not deal much damage, firestarters can deny large swaths of area.</description>
    <techLevel>Industrial</techLevel>
    <comps>
      <li Class="CompProperties_ApparelReloadable">
        <maxCharges>4</maxCharges>
        <ammoDef>Neutroamine</ammoDef>
        <ammoCountPerCharge>5</ammoCountPerCharge>
        <baseReloadTicks>120</baseReloadTicks>
